# 1) Forzar HTTPS y sin www
http://www.kelownaprotechmobilemech.com/*   https://kelownaprotechmobilemech.com/:splat   301!
https://www.kelownaprotechmobilemech.com/*  https://kelownaprotechmobilemech.com/:splat   301!

# 2) Aliases cortos → URL canónica de servicios
/diagnostic        /services/diagnostic/        301
/pre-purchase      /services/pre-purchase/      301
/maintenance       /services/maintenance/       301

# 3) Servir pretty URLs con y sin “/” (evita 404)
/services/diagnostic       /services/diagnostic/index.html       200
/services/diagnostic/      /services/diagnostic/index.html       200
/services/pre-purchase     /services/pre-purchase/index.html     200
/services/pre-purchase/    /services/pre-purchase/index.html     200
/services/maintenance      /services/maintenance/index.html      200
/services/maintenance/     /services/maintenance/index.html      200